detail_desc: Square-necked top in crinkled jersey with elastication at the shoulders and short puff sleeves with an elasticated, overlocked frill trim.
Longer, wide-fitting jumper in a soft knit containing some wool with long sleeves and wide ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.

Padded ski mittens in windproof, water-repellent functional fabric with folded seams and elasticated wrists with an adjustable hook and loop fastening. Thinsulate™ lining.The mittens have a water-repellent coating without fluorocarbons. Size 3-6M without thumbs.
Jumper in a soft knit containing some wool with a high, ribbed collar and zip with a round pull at the top. Low dropped shoulders, long, wide sleeves and wide ribbing at the cuffs and hem.
Jacquard-knit socks in a soft cotton blend.
Straight.cut jacket in soft faux fur with notch lapels, concealed press-studs down the front and side pockets. Lined.
Long-sleeved, all-in-one pyjamas in soft, organic cotton jersey.
Long-sleeved jumper in soft, fine-knit cotton with a knitted motif and pocket on the front and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Short-sleeved jersey top with a motif.
5-pocket skirt in washed denim with a high waist, button fly and frayed, raw-edge hem.
Wrapover blouse in an airy cotton weave with broderie anglaise. V-neck, concealed press-studs and ties at one side. Short, wide sleeves with a scalloped trim, and a scalloped neckline. Unlined.
Pull-on shorts in washed denim with elasticated ribbing and a drawstring at the waist. Fake fly, fake front pockets and real back pockets.
Short top in a soft, rib-knit viscose blend with narrow shoulder straps, a V-neck front and back and embroidery on the front.
Cropped top in soft, ribbed jersey with a V-neck, straight cut at the back and narrow shoulder straps.
Belt in grained leather with a metal buckle. Width 4 cm.
Ankle-length jeans in washed, stretch denim with a high waist, zip fly and button, back pockets and skinny legs. The cotton content of the jeans is partly recycled.
Joggers in lightweight sweatshirt fabric with wide elastication and a drawstring at the waist, and ribbed hems.
Long-sleeved jumper in a soft, fine knit containing some wool. Sewn-on lace collar and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem. The polyester in the jumper is recycled.
Trousers in ribbed jersey made from a viscose blend with a wide, elasticated waist and long, wide legs.
Long-sleeved top in sweatshirt fabric with a kangaroo pocket, hood with a wrapover front, and ribbing at the cuffs and hem. Soft brushed inside.
Sports vest top in fast-drying functional fabric with a racer back.
Platform sandals in suede with a braided jute trim, an adjustable ankle strap with a metal buckle, and wedge heels. Rubber soles. Platform front 3.5 cm, heel 9.5 cm.

Long-sleeved top in cotton sweatshirt fabric with a double-layered hood, dropped shoulders and long sleeves. Decorative, shaping seams at the front and back that continue down the sleeves and a rounded hem with inset ribbing at the front. Slightly longer at the back.
Satin top with a V-neck, lace trim at the top and narrow, adjustable shoulder straps.
Boxer shorts in cotton jersey with short legs, an elasticated waist and lined front. The cotton content of the shorts is organic.
Fully lined, lace-patterned bikini. Top with narrow, adjustable shoulder straps, one of which has a small metal decoration.
Top in soft sweatshirt fabric with gently dropped shoulders, long sleeves and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Thong briefs in lace with a mid waist, lined gusset and string back.
V-neck blouse in a jacquard weave with a drawstring and decorative gathers at the front and a seam with a flounce at the hem. Slightly shorter at the front.
Pattern-knit trainer socks in a cotton blend.
Sleeveless dress in printed cotton jersey with a gathered seam at the waist and flared skirt.
Fitted strappy top in soft cotton jersey with a lace-trimmed V-neck.
Knee socks knitted in chenille with elasticated tops.
Long bikini top in fluted, crinkled fabric with adjustable spaghetti shoulder straps and discreet elastication at the hem. Gathers in the sides and an inner top with an elasticated hem. No fasteners.
Round-necked T-shirt in sturdy cotton jersey.
Joggers in sweatshirt fabric with an elasticated drawstring waist, side pockets and ribbed hems. Soft brushed inside. The cotton content of the joggers is organic.
Lace body with narrow adjustable shoulder straps, a lined gusset with press-studs and a half-string back.
Top in a cotton weave with narrow shoulder straps and buttons down the front. Straight cut at the top with a foldover edge, a wide tie at the waist and a rounded hem.
Blouse in a soft weave with a narrow collar, concealed buttons down the front, long sleeves with buttoned cuffs and a rounded hem.
Skirt in several layers of tulle with a glittery elastic waistband.
Twill cap with a motif on the front, sweatband in a cotton weave and an adjustable plastic fastener at the back.
Calf-length skater skirt in a textured jersey knit with a high waist and concealed zip at the back. Unlined.
Metal necklace with pendants in the shape of a lock and key. The lock is decorated with a plastic bead. Adjustable length. The zinc content of the necklace is recycled.
Socks in a soft, jacquard-knit cotton blend with elasticated tops.
Joggers in slub cotton jersey with an elasticated drawstring waist, patch front pockets and ribbed hems.
Long, one-shoulder jumpsuit in viscose jersey with a seam and tie belt at the waist and pockets in the side seams. Loose fit with wide legs.
Elasticated scrunchies in a pleated weave.
5-pocket, ankle-length jeans in washed denim with a regular waist, button fly and slim, straight legs.
Long-sleeved body in soft, patterned, ribbed jersey with a V-neck front and back and concealed press-studs at the crotch.
Earrings in different designs with sparkly stone chains and shells. Length 11.5 and 16 cm.
Fitted top in a soft rib-knit viscose blend with a V-neck.
Joggers in lightweight sweatshirt fabric with a washed look. Elasticated, ribbed waist, a kangaroo pocket and ribbed hems. The cotton content of the joggers is organic.
Sunglasses with plastic and metal frames and UV-protective, tinted lenses.
Straight-cut shirt in woven fabric. Collar and buttons down the front, chest pocket and long sleeves with buttoned cuffs.
Sleeveless top in an airy cotton weave with a deep, flounce-trimmed V-neck front and back, pin-tucks at the top and a peplum at the hem. Unlined.
Long metal earrings with a hoop and a large plastic bead at the bottom. Length 8.3 cm.

Calf-length dress in an airy Tencel™ lyocell and viscose weave with a small stand-up collar and V-neck. Dropped shoulders, long sleeves with a slit and covered button at the cuffs, and a curved hem. Longer at the back. Unlined.
Shorts in imitation leather with a regular waist, face pockets and a visible zip at the front. Lined.
Shirt in a stretch cotton weave with a classic button front, yoke with a pleat at the back, long sleeves with buttoned cuffs and a rounded hem.
Joggers in sweatshirt fabric made from a cotton blend with an elasticated drawstring waist and side pockets. Narrow, decorative piping down the legs and ribbed hems. Soft brushed inside.
Metal bangles in different designs.
Scarf in a patterned weave that can also be tied as a hairband. Size 55x55 cm.

Short parka with a faux shearling-lined hood, high collar with a tab and press-stud and a concealed zip down the front. Handwarmer pockets at the top and patch front pockets with a flap, hook and loop fastening and an opening at the sides. Sleeves with a tab and press-stud at the cuffs, one sleeve with a pocket that has a flap and hook and loop fastening. Drawstring at the hem and a single back vent. Recycled polyester lining.
Boxer briefs in cotton jersey with a lined gusset.
Necklaces in various types of thin metal chain, one with leaf-shaped pendants. Adjustable length 40-54 cm.
Shorts in soft, printed cotton jersey with an elasticated drawstring waist.
Cardigan in a soft, jacquard knit containing some wool. Slightly longer style with gently dropped shoulders, long sleeves, front pockets and narrow ribbing at the cuffs and hem. No buttons.
T-shirt in soft cotton jersey with a printed front and round neckline with a narrow trim.
Patterned running tights in fast-drying, breathable functional fabric with an elasticated drawstring waist, small zipped pocket at the back and a zip at the hems.
Fully lined, patterned swimsuit with narrow shoulder straps, a frill at the top and decorative bows.
Short-sleeved sports top in fast-drying functional fabric.
Jumper in a soft, fine knit with plastic beads and hole embroidery on the shoulders.

Slightly longer blouse in an airy weave with a small stand-up collar, buttons down the front, a yoke with a pleat at the back and a rounded hem. Decorative gathers at the shoulders and long sleeves with buttoned cuffs.
Long-sleeved body in stretch jersey crêpe with press-studs at the crotch and an open back with a knot detail.
Jacket in supple suede with a collar, buttons down the front, flap chest pockets with a button and welt side pockets. Adjustable tab and button at the sides, and buttoned cuffs. Lined.
Short-sleeved polo shirt in patterned cotton piqué with a collar, button placket and short slits in the sides.
Sleeveless dress in soft, patterned cotton jersey with a gathered seam at the waist and flared skirt.
Wrapover cardigan in a soft, fine cotton knit with a button at the top and appliqué elbow patches.
Top in soft sweatshirt fabric with a motif on the front, dropped shoulders, long sleeves and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Jersey body with a V-neck, short cap sleeves and a lined gusset with press-studs.
